# Master Gitignore for Cricket-app

# Dependency directories
**/node_modules/
**/jspm_packages/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development.local
**/.env.test.local
**/.env.production.local
**/.env*.local

# Logs
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Build outputs
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/

# IDE files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.sublime-project
**/*.sublime-workspace
**/.DS_Store

# Static assets
**/uploads/
**/tmp/
**/temp/

# Misc
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock
